name: 0xpunks DAO Community
description:
Tired of project after project that makes you mint a bunch of pointless png images?
We have a chance to change this
1. Unless an NFT with high artistic value, it should be just a token to verify identity.
2. We create a token with no artistic value to verify your identity, all the value will be created by the community.
3. 100% of all income after deducting costs are placed in the community multi-signature wallet, so the operation of funds is left to the community to decide. Whether we want to go to the moon, buy land or invest.
payDisclosure: Join our discord to verify your identity and we will transfer the appropriate amount of tokens from Opensea to your wallet.
